@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jykevr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.abs(tmp + 0.60) / 0.99))
    tmp = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.95 * v1 + 0.31)) / wp.sin((v1 + 0.92 / v1 + 0.62)))
    v2 = wp.cos(tmp)
    v2 = v2
    tmp = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.27 - tmp + 0.80)) / (0.92 * (v0 + 0.00 - tmp + 0.67)))
    v1 = v0
    v2 = v2
    tmp = wp.cos(((v2 + 0.36 - v0 + 0.08) * 0.48))
    data[tid] = v0
